      <section>
        <h4>Summary of PAW</h4>
        PAW stands for Play and Win! The PAW team has partnered with game companies like Envoy, and these companies have donated games for the team to give away. The rules are simple- you play a donated game and become eligible to win it. The intent of the PAW Program is to get as many players as possible to check out a game they might not have played previously. One entry per player per game levels the field and makes everyone who has played it equally likely to win a game. It also encourages people to try out many different games. You can play any game you like as many times as you like, but we hope you try out many different games over the weekend, not just one.

        <br>
      </section>
